    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "私はまだ子供ですけど、お二人のおかげでセンターも\n経験出来て、少しずつ、成長出来てる気がします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I'm still a kid‚ thanks to you two‚ I've had the experience of\nbeing a center‚ and little by little‚ I feel like I've been able to grow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6688261948,
      "endTime": 12.6395992241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.9062618219
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "風邪引いた時も看病してくれて、ありがとうね～\n一緒に過ごした一つ一つが、大切な思い出です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for taking care of me when I caught a cold~\nEvery moment we spent together is a precious memory.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9062618219,
      "endTime": 21.5999979853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.3666646519
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.9116765939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "お二人と一緒なら、私達はどこまでも飛んでいけます\nこれからも、よろしくお願いしますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As long as we're together with you two‚ we can fly anywhere.\nPlease continue to support us in the future too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9116765939,
      "endTime": 29.231676574799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
